rComments: Prof. Loback is good at his craft.  He loves music and he instills that in students.  The university is clever to have procured his services.  He makes the difference in learning and LEARNING!!
Of all the teachers, in all of the schools . . . I had to walk into his class . . .and let Jamie Loback win my heart!
Jamie's a hotty. Going into music, i was completely lost. Jamie showed me the way, oh yeah. Thanks Jamie, thanks ;)
Since when is a prof a FRIEND????
Jamie is awesome, if he becomes famous one day i'll tell everyone 'i knew Jamie Loback' There's not a better friend than he.
You are the most classy prof around!
